Subject: RE: [VB] '59 Kombi...one night engine pull

When I sold my side loader, the new owner wanted a bigger engines and  FF
trans, so, we pulled my DD in the shop, pulled the side loader in behind it.
Me and my co-worker started in on a double engine and trans swap at around
noon and by 5 in the afternoon we drove both buses out. Two people, hoist,
air tools made things go fast.

ronnie

